37:35.987 --> 37:38.990
It wasn't easy at first,

37:38.990 --> 37:40.792
but I soon realized

37:40.792 --> 37:44.129
I still had
a lot of life to live.

37:44.129 --> 37:50.436
**

37:53.305 --> 37:56.074
