how to do it, Hugh!

38:06.618 --> 38:08.053
And, of course,

38:08.053 --> 38:10.822
the most beautiful
women in the world.

38:10.822 --> 38:15.093
Before I knew it,
in 2003,

38:15.093 --> 38:18.764
Playboy had reached
another milestone...

38:18.764 --> 38:20.265
**

38:20.265 --> 38:23.101
...our 50th anniversary.

38:23.101 --> 38:26.838
I could not have imagined,
on any kind of level,

38:26.838 --> 38:28.807
the impact
the magazine would have,

38:28.807 --> 38:31.109
how it would change
my life.

38:31.109 --> 38:33.845
Who could have imagined it?

38:35.881 --> 38:37.683
But the early 2000s

38:37.683 --> 38:40.185
brought something we could
have never expected...

38:40.185 --> 38:44.089
**

38:44.089 --> 38:46.057
...the Internet.

38:46.057 --> 38:48.293
**

38:48.293 --> 38:50.562
The rise of the Internet

38:50.562 --> 38:52.864
destroys the business
model of Playboy.

38:52.864 --> 38:57.603
There is no way that you
can sell printed material

38:57.603 --> 38:59.905
or even a channel

38:59.905 --> 39:02.908
when you have to compete
with free video,

39:02.908 --> 39:06.945
open access, and any
kind of porn you want.

39:06.945 --> 39:10.416
**

39:10.416 --> 39:12.117
But while we
couldn't compete

39:12.117 --> 39:15.854
with what was online,
there was one new trend

39:15.854 --> 39:18.757
that was a perfect fit
for Playboy.

39:18.757 --> 39:20.859
Welcome to
the Playboy Mansion.

39:20.859 --> 39:24.396
**

39:24.396 --> 39:28.667
And with reality TV
being all the rage,

39:28.667 --> 39:30.669
I knew it could be
the perfect way

39:30.669 --> 39:33.572
to move Playboy
into the 21st century.

39:33.572 --> 39:34.973
I invited the world

39:34.973 --> 39:38.209
into the Playboy Mansion
every week

39:38.209 --> 39:39.745
as the Playmates and I

39:39.745 --> 39:42.448
