Does it still work?

40:09.775 --> 40:12.177
People loved the girls.

40:12.177 --> 40:16.414
There was something relatable
about each of them.

40:16.414 --> 40:18.016
**

40:18.016 --> 40:19.885
It lasted six seasons

40:19.885 --> 40:23.354
and introduced Playboy
to a whole new generation,

40:23.354 --> 40:26.324
and it became one of
the most successful shows

40:26.324 --> 40:28.259
in the history
of E! Network,

40:28.259 --> 40:31.229
with over 2 million
viewers at its peak.

40:31.229 --> 40:32.664
**

40:32.664 --> 40:35.133
