in 2016.

42:18.269 --> 42:20.839
To this day, Playboy

42:20.839 --> 42:23.208
is the third-most
recognizable brand

42:23.208 --> 42:24.309
in the world,

42:24.309 --> 42:29.047
after only Apple
and Coca-Cola.

42:29.047 --> 42:30.982
I never
could have imagined

42:30.982 --> 42:35.386
