42:39.958 --> 42:43.762
**

42:43.762 --> 42:46.632
Looking back on my life,

42:46.632 --> 42:49.167
I see so many things.

42:49.167 --> 42:52.971
**

42:55.807 --> 42:58.143
What do you think
of this?

42:59.911 --> 43:03.014
Hefner is one of the
most underrated forces

43:03.014 --> 43:05.717
