44:21.326 --> 44:25.196
It was his ability
to deliver the message

44:25.196 --> 44:27.598
as well as promote
a conversation about it

44:27.598 --> 44:29.500
that was really
revolutionary.

44:29.500 --> 44:33.839
The magazine and the company
just became the messenger of,

44:33.839 --> 44:36.141
these are conversations
we should be having

44:36.141 --> 44:38.910
and these are topics we should
be thinking about a lot more.

44:38.910 --> 44:41.980
He didn't introduce
the world to sex.

44:41.980 --> 44:45.751
He just allowed it
to step out of the closet.

44:45.751 --> 44:48.453
Yes, yes.
Straight down the lens.

44:48.453 --> 44:49.821
Perfect.

44:49.821 --> 44:52.824
I think he was confident
of what he had done,

44:52.824 --> 44:56.094
